post_title: FS: one of these Del Howard uncataloged variations
post_content:
I want to keep one of these two so whichever one the first person to respond here or in a pm chooses I will be keeping the other one.

This is an uncataloged variation that I discovered several years ago that is similar to the known Pfeffer "CHICACO variation the Howard variation reads CHICAGC. Over the past several years I have found 11 out of 800+ Howards with this variation which is around 1.375%. Besides one of the two that is up for sale I'm posting images of a couple of the others that I've seen.

Price is for a no fees payment and includes shipping in a bubble mailer with tracking to a United States address.

A = $200 NLFS
B = $275 Sold
